Required for webpack

npm i -D react react-dom
npm i path
npm i -D webpack webpack-cli @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/preset-react babel-loader
npm i -D html-webpack-plugin html-loader
npm i -D webpack-dev-server
npm i -D prettier
npm i -D parcel-bundler

Required for Client

npm i @emotion/css
npm i @reach/router

Required for server

npm i express
npm i http
npm i path
npm i fs
npm i body-parser
npm i multer
npm i os
npm i mongoose
npm i nodemailer
npm i pdfkit
npm i jsonwebtoken
npm i winston
npm i bcrypt
npm i winston

Must first run 'npm run start' and then start the node server.


